   "source": [
    "### 3.Data Preprocessing\n",
    ".Lower case\n",
    ".Tokenization\n",
    ".Removing special characters\n",
    ".Removing stop words and punctuation\n",
    ".Stemming"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 199,
   "id": "74849994",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "hi i will be home you want someth\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ps = PorterStemmer()\n",
    "\n",
    "def transform_text(text):\n",
    "    text = text.lower()\n",
    "    text= nltk.word_tokenize(text)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    y=[]\n",
    "    for i in text:\n",
    "        if i.isalnum():\n",
    "            y.append(i)\n",
    "            \n",
    "    text = y[:]\n",
    "    y.clear()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for i in text:\n",
    "        y.append(ps.stem(i))\n",
    "        \n",
    "    return \" \".join(y)\n",
    "\n",
    "t_text = transform_text(\"Hi! I will be home tonight.Do you want something ?\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(t_text)"
   ]
  },

    "import pickle\n",
    "from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\n",
    "from sklearn.naive_bayes import MultinomialNB\n",
    "\n",
    "X_train = [\"Sample text 1\", \"Sample text 2\", \"Sample text 3\"]\n",
    "y_train = [0, 1, 0]\n",
    "\n",
    "tfidf = TfidfVectorizer(lowercase=True, stop_words='english')\n",
    "X_train_tfidf = tfidf.fit_transform(X_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "mnb = MultinomialNB()\n",
    "mnb.fit(X_train_tfidf, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "with open('vectorizer2.pkl', 'wb') as vectorizer_file:\n",
    "    pickle.dump(tfidf, vectorizer_file)\n",
    "\n",
    "with open('model2.pkl', 'wb') as model_file:\n",
    "    pickle.dump(mnb, model_file)\n"
   ]
  },

    "import pickle\n",
    "from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\n",
    "from sklearn.naive_bayes import MultinomialNB\n",
    "\n",
    "X_train = [\"Sample text 1\", \"Sample text 2\", \"Sample text 3\"]\n",
    "y_train = [0, 1, 0]\n",
    "\n",
    "tfidf = TfidfVectorizer(lowercase=True, stop_words='english')\n",
    "X_train_tfidf = tfidf.fit_transform(X_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "mnb = MultinomialNB()\n",
    "mnb.fit(X_train_tfidf, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "with open('vectorizer.pkl', 'wb') as vectorizer_file:\n",
    "    pickle.dump(tfidf, vectorizer_file)\n",
    "\n",
    "with open('model1.pkl', 'wb') as model_file:\n",
    "    pickle.dump(mnb, model_file)\n"
   ]
  }
